# Window warping using Alt+hjkl & Alt+Shift+hjkl

# Horizontal+Vertical movement
Key H	A $[Mod1]2 Window-Warp-LeftCenter
Key J	A $[Mod1]2 Window-Warp-CenterBottom
Key K	A $[Mod1]2 Window-Warp-CenterTop
Key L	A $[Mod1]2 Window-Warp-RightCenter

Key H	A $[Mod2]2 Window-Warp-LeftTop
Key J	A $[Mod2]2 Window-Warp-LeftBottom
Key K	A $[Mod2]2 Window-Warp-RightTop
Key L	A $[Mod2]2 Window-Warp-RightBottom

# vim:ft=fvwm
